    <h1>Return Policy</h1>
    <p class="effective-date">Effective Date: October 2025</p>

    <h2>Returns and Refunds</h2>
    <p>You may return most new, unused items within 30 days of delivery for a full refund. Items must be in their original packaging and condition.</p>

    <h2>Non-returnable Items</h2>
    <ul>
      <li>Final sale or limited edition drops</li>
      <li>Items that have been worn, washed, or altered</li>
      <li>Gift cards</li>
    </ul>

    <h2>How to Return</h2>
    <p>To initiate a return, contact our support team at
      <a href="mailto:support@snehvastra.store">support@snehvastra.store</a>
      with your order details. We’ll guide you through the return process.
    </p>

    <h2>Refunds</h2>
    <p>Refunds are processed within <strong>7–10 business days</strong> after we receive your returned item. All refunds will be made to your original payment method.</p>

    <h2>Exchanges</h2>
    <p>We currently do not offer direct exchanges. To exchange an item, please return it and place a new order for the desired product.</p>
